{{Quote|Remember how I told you that a Sacorrian woman is not allowed to marry without her father's consent, no matter how old she is?''"<br />"''Yes, what about it?''"<br />"''Well, there's just one thing. We don't have to do anything about it ''immediately'', but there's something more I want to tell you about that law. An interesting legal technicality. It's been well established by many precedents that a Sacorrian woman is not bound by that law&mdash;''if'' she is outside the Sacorrian system.|[[Tendra Risant Calrissian|Tendra Risant]] and [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]]|<ref name="Showdown at Centerpoint">''[[Showdown at Centerpoint]]''</ref>}}
The '''Sacorrian system''' was home to the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Sacorria]]. The system was considered to be an [[Outlier systems|Outlier]] of the Corellian sector.

